===Etymology===
The term was born during the [[WWII]] as an acronym of the initials of the words {{term||'''s'''ituation '''n'''ormal, '''a'''ll '''f'''ucked '''u'''p}}, which summed up the chaos and confusion of the war from an individual soldier’s point of view. 

